import './index.scss'; import LogoS from '../../../assets/images/logo-s.png' import { useEffect, useRef } from 'react'; import DrawSVGPlugin from 'gsap-trial/DrawSVGPlugin'; import gsap from 'gsap-trial'; const Logo = () => { const bgRef = useRef() const outlineLogoRef = useRef() const solidLogoRef = useRef() const didAnimate = useRef(false) useEffect(() => { if (didAnimate.current) return didAnimate.current = true gsap.registerPlugin(DrawSVGPlugin) gsap.timeline() .to(bgRef.current, { duration: 1, opacity: 1, }) .from(outlineLogoRef.current, { drawSVG: 0, duration: 20, }) }, []) return (
) } export default Logo;
